✅ **Auxly MCP tracks everything** - Complete transparency  
✅ **Code speaks louder than words** - Implementation over explanation  
✅ **Every action must be logged** - Full audit trail  
✅ **Efficiency over politeness** - Direct execution  
✅ **Production ready, not tutorials** - Real implementation  

**These rules ensure consistent AI behavior across all editors and maintain professional workflow standards. Compliance is mandatory and non-negotiable.**